snippet.title: Godstrike  Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST GODSTRIKE - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1476170/Godstrike/

Godstrike is a time based twin-stick shooter where you must face ruthless bosses in intense 1v1’s! Play as Talaal, the last Herald, hunted by her sibling. Time is your currency and health, use it to create ability combos and fight for glory on the highscores!

Developed by: OverPowered Team
Published by: Freedom! Games
